{"tid":1179730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑪利諾神父教會學校校友會有限公司: 對外發表「反對政府修訂【逃犯條例】」的聯署聲明是一小撮人的獨斷行為","createTime":"2019-05-31T10:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T10:37:55.000Z","uid":137704,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b5b75d92908dd81fd1bf6e338334a0681aa31b","tid":1179730,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"*瑪利諾神父教會學校校友會有限公司（成立於2004年）嚴正聲明*：<br />\n<br />\n近日有人/組織以「瑪利諾神父教會學校校友、師生」名義，對外發表「反對政府修訂【逃犯條例】」的聯署聲明，本會認清那是一小撮人的獨斷行為，不能代表我們眾多校友及師生的意願，特此作出澄清及聲明，以正視聽；並已提請母校進行調查，予以嚴正處理，以保護本校同學寧靜之學習環境，免被別有用心之政治紛擾及汚染。<br />\n<br />\n瑪利諾神父教會學校校友會有限公司<br />\n（成立於2004年） <br />\n會長 吳慕德<br />\n2019年5月30日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MaryknollFathersSchoolAlumniLimited/posts/2171219016318738?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARCQLQVd_pjPYaJ8JFZeE7s4qwFdTCNiMAbEP4ddv0u0O6diwlrJayRDjknp4PRj6fhblDmC4LT6aMO3vWoLbQu0TGrMq_1bW6TdKtpcYewpJBAO3DSm3-8EBu0kmj-sAJlZAWDu18suVTs1qibdT9AOnUIwJtSLduNgw-wot8YpWB5_QEIoLOiHkA2yjn__a7Z-ib3iZPO_cfKSu0wKEj8rr5u_XBGNCx4Oci2OGUbLA8jC97k3EhODYjA41Z0rX1euMaME2mX2tDDMpwrjoOGjkbV2PMt2YRvhEesU15N5iFdR61wEIADVWUpvzdqyLIEg983pQ9h5OfHJHc7TrA&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMaryknollFathersSchoolAlumniLimited%2Fposts%2F2171219016318738%3F__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARCQLQVd_pjPYaJ8JFZeE7s4qwFdTCNiMAbEP4ddv0u0O6diwlrJayRDjknp4PRj6fhblDmC4LT6aMO3vWoLbQu0TGrMq_1bW6TdKtpcYewpJBAO3DSm3-8EBu0kmj-sAJlZAWDu18suVTs1qibdT9AOnUIwJtSLduNgw-wot8YpWB5_QEIoLOiHkA2yjn__a7Z-ib3iZPO_cfKSu0wKEj8rr5u_XBGNCx4Oci2OGUbLA8jC97k3EhODYjA41Z0rX1euMaME2mX2tDDMpwrjoOGjkbV2PMt2YRvhEesU15N5iFdR61wEIADVWUpvzdqyLIEg983pQ9h5OfHJHc7TrA%26__tn__%3D-R&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=4344398e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MaryknollFathersSchoolAlumniLimited/posts/2171219016318738?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARCQLQVd_pjPYaJ8JFZeE7s4qwFdTCNiMAbEP4ddv0u0O6diwlrJayRDjknp4PRj6fhblDmC4LT6aMO3vWoLbQu0TGrMq_1bW6TdKtpcYewpJBAO3DSm3-8EBu0k